Bodyweight Exercise: 60 sec rest between sets
1. Birddog 10x - 3 sets 2. Deadbugs 15x - 3 sets 3. Squats 9x - 2 sets 4. Glute Bridges 11x - 2 sets 5. Rows/Reverse Push-ups 12x - 2 sets 6. Push-ups 12x - 2 sets
Brisk five-minute warmup walk, then jog 4km (or 25 minutes).
